#

Decadent Dark Chocolate Mousse Cake

50 min
$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

dairyeggs

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

dessert

Tags:

dessertchocolatecakemousse

Description

Indulge in this rich and creamy dark chocolate mousse cake, perfect for any celebration or a simple dessert treat!

Ingredients

  • dark chocolate: 8 oz
  • butter: 1/2 cup
  • sugar: 3/4 cup
  • eggs: 3
  • vanilla extract: 1 tsp
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • powdered sugar: 1/4 cup
  • cocoa powder: 2 tbsp
  • salt: a pinch
